<HEAD>Honduras Says Central American Peace Difficult Without
U.S.-U.S.S.R Help</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By GEORGE GEDDA</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>UNITED NATIONS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
