<HEAD>Tentative Accord Reached in Suit Over Government Mind Control
Research</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: INSERTS 4 grafs after 15th graf pvs bgng, `Two years,' to
UPDATE with additional details on Weinstein</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By JAMES ROWLEY</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
