<HEAD>Stalled Contract Talks Spur Strike by Chrysler Workers</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: UPDATES throughout with new information</NOTE>
<DATELINE>FENTON, Mo. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
